---
title: Welcome
description: Watch as Troy Vassalotti learns his way around a computer.
pageName: home
home: true
---
{% extends 'layouts/base.njk' %}

{% block content %}
    <main class="layout">
        <div class="hero">
            <div class="wrapper flex">
                <section class="welcome-screen" id="welcome">
                    <div class="typewriter-container">
                        <h1 class="typewriter typewriter_1">Hey, I'm Troy...</h1>
                        <p class="typewriter typewriter_2">...this is a website.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="portrait">
                        {% image './src/assets/img/me-on-set.jpg', 'A picture of me holding my guitar', [300, 600], ['webp', 'jpg'], '(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 50vw', 'full', 'me', 'eager' %}
                    </div>
                    <div class="content">
                        <p>I'm glad you could make it. Peruse my wares* and <a href="/about/">send me a letter</a> if
                            you're
                            so inclined.</p>
                        <p class="disclaimer">I only accept bottlecaps as currency, sorry... (I'm kidding)</p>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <section class="feed" id="posts">
                    <h2>Recent Posts</h2>
                    <div class="posts-section">
                        <div class="grid full">
                            {%- for post in collections.post.slice(collections.post.length - 5, collections.post.length) | reverse -%}
                                <article class="post-listing">
                                    <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
                                    <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
                                </article>
                            {%- endfor -%}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <a class="button" href="/posts/">View All Posts</a>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
        <section class="projects-section" id="projects">
            <div class="wrapper">
                <h2><span id="cool-anim">Latest</span> <span id="proj-anim">Projects</span></h2>
                <div class="showcase-container">
                    <div class="showcase">
                        {% for work in collections['work'] | reverse %}
                            <figure class="caption-overlay">
                                <a class="caption-link" href="{{ work.url }}">
                                     {% image "https://screenshot.troyv.dev/" + work.data.website | urlencode + "/opengraph", work.data.title + " Screenshot", [300, 800, 1200], ['webp', 'jpg'], '(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 1200px', 'caption-image full has-box-shadow' %}
                                    <div class="caption">
                                        <figcaption>
                                            <h3>{{ work.data.title }}</h3>
                                        </figcaption>
                                    </div>
                                </a>
                            </figure>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                    <section class="flex-center col center content">
                        <div class="skewed-background">
                            <div class="content">
                                <p>This only some of what I've been up to, but you can see <a href="/work/">everything
                                        else I've been doing</a> too.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="supplemental" id="more">
            <div id="clouds">
                <div class="cloud foreground"></div>
                <div class="cloud background"></div>
                <div class="cloud foreground"></div>
                <div class="cloud background"></div>
                <div class="cloud foreground"></div>
                <div class="cloud background"></div>
                <div class="cloud background"></div>
                <div class="cloud foreground"></div>
                <div class="cloud background"></div>
                <div class="cloud background"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="wrapper">
                <div class="sundial">
                    <button title="Turn the clouds animation on or off." id="sundial" type="button" name="sundial">
                        <img class="sun" src="/assets/img/sun.svg" alt="">
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="content">
                    <div class="music-section" id="music">
                        <h2>I Also Have Music</h2>
                        <p>When Iâ€™m not coding, maybe I'm writing. My friends and I started <span
                                    class="bold">Front Royal</span> with the desire to make a name for ourselves, and I
                            started <span class="bold">troy.</span> to explore a new outlet.</p>
                        <a class="button" href="/music/">Peek That Music</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="about-section" id="about">
                        <h2>Looking For More?</h2>
                        <p>You can probably find it on my <a href="/about/">about</a> page.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
